#app-welcome(class="flex h-screen overflow-hidden")
    .welcome-wrapper(class="p-2 m-auto")
        .welcome-title-messsage(class="text-2xl text-center") 
            |Connect with Another Device
             
        .welcome-image(class="text-3xl text-center")
            img(src="/public/assets/svg/img.svg",class="m-auto mt-1")

        .welcome-message(class="w-4/5 m-auto text-center")    
            |Share files,links,text,notes,images, between your devices with ease.

        .welcome-choice(class="mt-6")
            .connect
                button(class="self-center block w-4/5 p-2 m-auto mt-2 mb-2 text-white bg-indigo-700 rounded ") 
                    |Create Code  
            .create
                button(class="self-center block w-4/5 p-2 m-auto text-center border-2 border-black rounded 700") 
                    |Enter Code 